config BR2_PACKAGE_BCM20702_FIRMWARE
	bool "bcm20702-firmware (Broadcom BT dongle firmware)"
	help
	  Broadcom BCM20702 Bluetooth adapter patch-RAM firmware
	  (brcm/BCM20702A1-0b05-17cb.hcd), which btbcm uploads to
	  BCM20702-based USB Bluetooth dongles at power-up -- the common
	  ASUS USB-BT400 (0b05:17cb) and compatible generics. Without it
	  those dongles enumerate but never initialise.

	  Stock-parity firmware (35000 bytes, matching stock exactly),
	  fetched hash-pinned at BUILD TIME from
	  winterheart/broadcom-bt-firmware and NEVER committed to git.
	  This is Broadcom's proprietary firmware, redistributed the same
	  way as xow_dongle.bin -- see docs/decisions/0003-xone-firmware.md
	  and docs/firmware-parity.md.
